     <td align="center" width="120" bgcolor="#dddddd"><font class="GraphicCaption">"I wasn't allowed to attend this FanFaire. Someone needed to stay behind and feed Absor's pet monkey."</font></td>
     <td bgcolor="#ffffff"><img src="images/spacer.gif"></td>
